---
const waLink = "https://wa.me/628159203331?text=Halo%2C%20saya%20mau%20konsultasi%20website%20dan%20klaim%20diskon%2010%25.";
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 px-4 bg-dark text-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="text-accent text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider">✦ ✦ ✦</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="reveal text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-6 mb-4">
      Siap punya website<br />yang profesional?
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Konsultasi gratis, tanpa kewajiban order. Ceritakan kebutuhan kamu, kami bantu carikan solusi terbaik.
    </p>

    <!-- Urgency insentif -->
    <div class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-accent/10 border border-accent/30 text-accent rounded-xl px-5 py-3 mb-8 text-sm font-semibold">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
      </svg>
      Daftar bulan ini — dapatkan diskon 10% untuk 10 pendaftar pertama!
    </div>

    <div class="reveal">
      <a
        href={waLink}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-8 py-4 bg-wa text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-wa-dark transition-colors text-lg no-underline shadow-lg shadow-wa/25"
      >
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a9.9 9.9 0 0 0-8.5 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.4A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Zm0 18.1c-1.6 0-3.1-.4-4.4-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.1 8.1 0 1 1 12 20.1Zm4.5-6c-.2-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.5.1-.2.2-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.6 6.6 0 0 1-3.3-2.9c-.2-.4.2-.4.7-1.3 0-.2 0-.3-.1-.4l-.8-1.9c-.2-.5-.4-.4-.5-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.4.1-.7.3-.2.3-.9.9-.9 2.1s.9 2.5 1 2.6c.1.2 1.8 2.7 4.3 3.8.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.6.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2l-.4-.3Z"/></svg>
        Chat WhatsApp Sekarang
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="reveal text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">Balas cepat jam 08.00–21.00 WIB</p>
  </div>
</section>
